(7. Acceptance Criteria) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(The project shall be considered complete when users can securely log in, farms can be created) Tj T*
(and managed, sensors display real-time data, automatic irrigation works based on configured) Tj T*
(thresholds, manual irrigation controls function correctly, dashboard displays all required) Tj T*
(metrics, observation count is shown on the Owner Dashboard, yield variance never displays a) Tj T*
(negative value, tasks are sorted by Due Date, reports can be exported as PDF and Excel,) Tj T*
(notifications are sent successfully, APIs meet the defined performance requirements, and the) Tj T*
(system passes User Acceptance Testing with no critical defects.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
